    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks! That's well above my current level of understanding <span aria-label=\"sweat smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f605\" role=\"img\" title=\"sweat smile\">:sweat_smile:</span> but at least I can move forward...<br>\nBtw, I've read quite a number of chapters of TPL, MIL and FPL explaining the type hierarchy but I don't think I've ever encountered an explanation of what <code>Type*</code> means exactly. Do you have any pointer by chance?</p>",
